These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, electrician, manager, coach
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, egyptian, thai, turkish
1. the egyptian is on the left of the chinese##1
2. the teacher is the turkish##1
3. the thai is on the right of the chinese##1
4. the electrician is on the left of the turkish##1
5. the coach is on the left of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Job          | coach | manager | electrician | teacher   |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | chinese     | thai   | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee, fanta, cola
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, soccer, swimming, volleyball
1. the person drinking cola is the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | fanta | cola | coffee | sprite    |
| Sport   | swimming    | soccer      | parkour | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, rock-climbing, traveling, writing
House: farmhouse, victorian, wooden, colonial
1. the wooden house is on the left of the colonial house##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the farmhouse house##1
3. the victorian house is on the far right##1
4. the colonial house is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | fishing | writing | traveling   | rock-climbing |
| House   | farmhouse   | wooden | colonial | victorian         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, strawberry, orange, spinach
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, sailing, surfing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person eating spinach##1
2. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating mango##1
4. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Food   | spinach | strawberry | mango  | orange      |
| Sport         | sailing | tennis   | surfing | basketball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, cucumber, kiwi, pineapple
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, dunhill, blend, pall-mall
1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | pineapple | kiwi | cucumber | cauliflower |
| Cigar    | baccarat       | pall-mall | blend | dunhill     |

