.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, mexican, nigerian, pakistani
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary, martial-arts, satire
1. the mexican is on the far right##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | nigerian | dutch | mexican |
| Movie-Genre           | adventure      | martial-arts | satire | documentary    |

