.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, banana, corn, garlic
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, mouse, rat
1. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
2. the person eating garlic is on the far right##1
3. the person eating corn is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1
5. the person eating banana is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Food   | corn | banana | lime | garlic  |
| Pet           | mouse | chinchilla | rat       | ferret |

