.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, designer, entrepreneur, musician
City: berlin, rome, nizza, london
1. the person traveling to london is on the right of the designer##1
2. the person traveling to london is the musician##1
3. the designer is on the right of the chef##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
5. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | entrepreneur | chef      | designer | musician |
| City   | berlin          | rome | nizza     | london    |

