.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, spy, zombie
4 different pets are kept: goat, horse, mouse, goldfish
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | spy       | family | zombie   |
| Pet     | horse | mouse | goldfish   | goat |

