.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, october, june, november
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | cola | milk  | hot-chocolate | sprite |
| Birthday   | november | june | october          | may    |

