3. the person drinking sprite is the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | sprite | juice  | coffee | water   |
| Movie-Genre        | time-travel | musical | fantasy    | sports |

