.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, d&b, techno, soul
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, drama, scientific, spy
1. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of soul##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is the fan of techno##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
5. the person watching action movies is on the left of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre         | d&b | techno | soul | blues |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | scientific    | action      | drama   |

